data.description: Open House, Saturday, 03/02/2024! Text Zach Maxey to 59559 for more information or to book your private showing today! Amazing opportunity in well-established Jacob Farms Swim & Tennis Community! This lovely 4 bed 3 full bath two-story craftsman features an oversized LOFT, full bedroom and bathroom on the main, light and airy floorplan with dramatic two-story foyer and overhead Loft upon entry! Built in 2018, this home is better than new construction with a well established neighborhood. A stones throw away from Tribble Mill Park & Historic Freemans Mill Park (Alcovy River access) & which features over 700 Acres of local area amenities that include a fishing lake (non-motorized boats allowed), boat ramp, Ozora Meadows, accommodates up to 3,500 people for large events, playground and Alcovy River Access. Publix & Shopping are less than 5 minutes from the property, Hwy 316 & Sugarloaf Pwky are minutes away! NEW Improvements to your new home include but are not limited to: Freshly Painted Interior, Oak Handrailing w/ Cast Iron baluster upgrade, New Wide Plank Hardwood floors, New Decorative Light Fixtures Throughout! This large 4 be pristine condition could not present a more move in ready opportunity. OVERSIZED Kitchen Island and even a dedicated appliance barn/coffee station! Flat Level crisp and well maintained lot!
